  "text": "The method for this experiment was modelled on a study carried out by [CITATION_1] . They used a free verbal response method in which a series of stimuli was presented and participants wrote down a description of what they saw for each stimulus. They presented 12 stimuli. In this experiment, 10 stimuli were presented, 4 drawn from sets 1 and 2 of experiment 1, and the other 6 functioning as control/filler stimuli.",
